{
  "texts": [
    "It has the following supporting technologies for data acquisition and representation:",
    "Data collection technology NDT data are large and rich and have high granularity.",
    "To ensure the synchronization between DTN and the actual network, the NDT should accurately perceive massive heterogeneous data based on the specific requirements of network autonomy scenarios.",
    "It should dynamically adjust the scale of collected data according to changes in the network to avoid data redundancy and large data overhead.",
    "6G network data have the characteristics of multi-source heterogeneity and loose organization structure, making it challenging to efficiently obtain data from various application scenarios (Raj et al., 2023)."
  ]
}